# 🌌 About

OrbitVision-System is an advanced aerospace-focused platform that combines:

* 🛰️ Orbital simulation
* 🤖 Artificial Intelligence
* 👁️ Computer Vision
* 📡 Telemetry analytics
* 🚁 Drone swarm intelligence
* 🌍 Real-time visualization

Built for developers, researchers, aerospace enthusiasts, and students interested in intelligent aerospace systems.

---

# ✨ Features

## 🛰️ Orbital Systems

* Real-time orbit simulation
* Satellite trajectory tracking
* Aerospace visualization
* Orbital analytics

## 🤖 AI Vision

* Object detection
* AI recognition systems
* Drone vision analysis
* Computer vision pipelines

## 📡 Telemetry Dashboard

* Live monitoring
* Sensor analytics
* Mission statistics
* Data visualization

## 🚁 Drone Swarm Simulation

* Swarm coordination
* Autonomous movement
* Multi-agent simulation
* AI behavior systems

